      "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body" : "to avoid grabbing the mutex twice in a row in the request tracker, could call `.CountActiveConnections` only once:\r\n```\r\n        if (auto connections = g_requests.CountActiveConnections(); connections != 0) {\r\n            LogPrint(BCLog::HTTP, \"Waiting for %d connections to stop HTTP server\\n\", connections);\r\n        }\r\n```",
